    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/1a123d009e9b01f539c841818b311549.avif?t=1763838557\" width=616 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To Kill a God is an action roguelike set in the Death Spiral, a cursed realm where warriors are trapped in endless cycles of death and rebirth. As a Traveler, your only hope is to escape, but first, you must slay the gods who guard the way out.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/1ac437892372ec95ee8e5e382391d03d.poster.avif?t=1763838557\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/1ac437892372ec95ee8e5e382391d03d.webm?t=1763838557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/1ac437892372ec95ee8e5e382391d03d.mp4?t=1763838557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/3341ffb21d677e025fb1ec293b9e384e.avif?t=1763838557\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The heart of To Kill a God lies in the SkillMap System,  where the game’s map is your skill tree. Every path you carve, every node you unlock, and every route you choose defines your character’s power and playstyle.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/7c1d01e4c8731b84321893c31cbd74b5.poster.avif?t=1763838557\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/7c1d01e4c8731b84321893c31cbd74b5.webm?t=1763838557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/7c1d01e4c8731b84321893c31cbd74b5.mp4?t=1763838557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/fc94726a3754f38cd48d0a0c2cb0765d.avif?t=1763838557\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat in To Kill a God is fast, fluid, and unforgiving. Master the art of battle, combining your unique skill set to crush hordes of enemies and conquer powerful bosses. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/670ca5638b3dec5b49c7006dc0532ed3.poster.avif?t=1763838557\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/670ca5638b3dec5b49c7006dc0532ed3.webm?t=1763838557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/670ca5638b3dec5b49c7006dc0532ed3.mp4?t=1763838557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/9b38f03520195b68a3db1fb456e14432.avif?t=1763838557\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect loot, combine skills, and craft enhancements to perfect your build. Experiment with different recipes to discover your preferred path to greatness.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/4413eb6b94e287825aaafbbf49fa4018.poster.avif?t=1763838557\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/4413eb6b94e287825aaafbbf49fa4018.webm?t=1763838557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/4413eb6b94e287825aaafbbf49fa4018.mp4?t=1763838557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/828cf8ec1c59754917b1b67fc93db7ed.avif?t=1763838557\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a twisted realm where forgotten warriors, mad cults, and tyrannical demigods battle for power. Uncover the secrets of the Death Spiral and the fallen gods on your quest to escape the cycle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/679526f127005e08ff87c2380c3c9698.poster.avif?t=1763838557\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/679526f127005e08ff87c2380c3c9698.webm?t=1763838557\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3261920/extras/679526f127005e08ff87c2380c3c9698.mp4?t=1763838557\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Developer Note: Progress will not carry over to the final game</strong></p>",
